WEBVTT

00:06.000 --> 00:12.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

01:59.419 --> 02:00.852
I can tell you like it.

02:00.987 --> 02:01.976
Oh.

02:02.122 --> 02:03.350
I love it.

02:03.490 --> 02:04.479
It's perfect.

02:04.624 --> 02:05.613
Well, great.

02:05.758 --> 02:07.191
It really is such a neat place.

02:07.494 --> 02:10.952
You know, I showed it
to another girl this morning.

02:11.097 --> 02:13.190
But to be honest,
I didn't like her very much.

02:13.333 --> 02:14.664
She looks like trouble,

02:14.801 --> 02:18.760
and I'm way too old to be
dealing with all that nonsense.

02:18.872 --> 02:22.171
I go a lot on my gut feelings,
and I have a good one about you.

02:22.308 --> 02:24.208
You remind me of my daughter.

02:24.344 --> 02:26.141
Oh, thank you.

02:26.279 --> 02:29.180
It's just what
I've been looking for.

02:29.315 --> 02:30.304
Well, great.

02:30.450 --> 02:36.286
Welcome to your new home.

02:48.468 --> 02:50.732
I'll get things moving
on your application,

02:50.870 --> 02:55.034
and we'll have you set up here
in no time.

02:55.175 --> 02:59.544
Um, about the deposit, um....

02:59.679 --> 03:01.146
Okay, I'll tell you what.

03:01.247 --> 03:03.647
If it'll help you out,
and I imagine it would,

03:03.750 --> 03:05.809
I'll agree to waive
all of the deposit stuff.

03:05.919 --> 03:07.716
You just give me
the first month's down.

03:07.854 --> 03:09.014
We'll call it a day, all right?

03:09.155 --> 03:10.144
Really?

03:10.256 --> 03:11.587
That would be incredible.

03:11.724 --> 03:14.022
Well, I remember when
my daughter was looking

03:14.160 --> 03:15.525
for her first apartment.

03:15.662 --> 03:17.562
It's hard coming up
with all that money, isn't it?

03:17.697 --> 03:18.721
You just promise me

03:18.865 --> 03:21.231
that you are gonna take
good care of this place.

03:21.367 --> 03:22.391
I promise.

03:22.535 --> 03:24.230
Besides,
you'll be a good tenant.

03:24.370 --> 03:25.769
I always trust my gut.

03:25.905 --> 03:28.169
Well, you won't regret it.
I swear.

03:28.274 --> 03:30.765
Oh, you know,
I have some things

03:30.910 --> 03:33.743
I have to still take care of
with the gal that lives here.

03:33.880 --> 03:35.404
You just get me the check
by Monday.

03:35.548 --> 03:36.879
I'll have you in by the end
of the week,

03:37.016 --> 03:38.347
if that's okay with you.

03:38.451 --> 03:39.440
I can do whatever.

03:39.586 --> 03:40.575
Good.

03:40.720 --> 03:41.778
Thank you so much.

03:41.921 --> 03:43.513
You bet, sweetie.
Bye-bye.

07:05.825 --> 07:08.225
Heather, come on.

07:08.327 --> 07:11.387
It's morning.

08:27.073 --> 08:29.234
Please leave a message
after the beep.

08:30.877 --> 08:32.366
Hi.

08:32.511 --> 08:33.570
This is Samantha Hughes.

08:33.712 --> 08:36.682
I'm calling in regards
to the babysitter flyer

08:36.816 --> 08:39.683
posted outside my dorm.

08:39.818 --> 08:41.376
I hope this is the right number.

08:41.520 --> 08:46.049
If it is, you can reach me
at 815-1920.

08:46.192 --> 08:47.659
I'm very interested.

08:47.760 --> 08:49.887
Thank you.

09:26.065 --> 09:27.123
Hello?

09:27.266 --> 09:28.563
Samantha.

09:28.701 --> 09:30.225
Yes?

09:30.369 --> 09:34.738
You just left me a message
about the babysitting position.

09:34.874 --> 09:37.604
Oh, yeah, I did.

09:37.743 --> 09:39.643
How did you get this number?

09:39.779 --> 09:43.408
Please excuse the urgency,
but if you're still interested,

09:43.549 --> 09:45.278
I would like to meet you.

09:45.418 --> 09:48.478
Sure.
That would be fine.

09:48.621 --> 09:50.248
Well, I'm afraid
I'm not too familiar

09:50.389 --> 09:51.447
with the layout over there.

09:51.591 --> 09:52.580
Perhaps you could meet me

09:52.725 --> 09:55.159
in front
of the Student Affairs office?

09:55.294 --> 09:57.558
That's where I dropped off
my advertisements.

09:57.663 --> 10:00.131
Okay, I know where that is.

10:00.266 --> 10:01.460
Wonderful.

10:01.601 --> 10:03.262
I'll see you there.

10:03.402 --> 10:07.668
Right now?

10:07.807 --> 10:09.672
Hello?

11:13.639 --> 11:15.402
Psst.

11:44.170 --> 11:46.070
All right, everyone.

11:48.340 --> 11:50.103
Have a great holiday.
I'll see you guys next year.

11:50.242 --> 11:53.109
Whoo-hoo.
Whoo.

13:39.852 --> 13:41.877
So tell me all about it.

13:42.021 --> 13:45.650
I want details.

13:45.791 --> 13:48.055
Well, it's not too big.

13:48.194 --> 13:49.491
When you walk in,

13:49.628 --> 13:52.620
there's, like, a little
living room area on the left

13:52.731 --> 13:53.959
and then a hallway
down the right.

13:54.066 --> 13:55.363
Oh, it is carpet or hardwood?

13:55.501 --> 13:56.525
Hardwood.

13:56.669 --> 13:57.658
Good.

13:57.803 --> 13:59.168
Carpet's filth,

13:59.305 --> 14:01.705
especially for a germaphobe
like you.

14:01.841 --> 14:04.139
I'm not a germaphobe.

14:05.311 --> 14:06.369
What?

14:06.512 --> 14:08.878
I don't like gross things.

14:09.014 --> 14:10.982
Anyway,
the kitchen's kind of blah,

14:11.083 --> 14:12.175
and so is the bathroom.

14:12.318 --> 14:14.718
But I'll paint them cool colors
or something.

14:14.854 --> 14:15.843
Yeah.

14:15.988 --> 14:18.388
Oh.

14:18.524 --> 14:19.684
I wish you had pictures.

14:19.825 --> 14:21.019
Yeah, me too.

14:21.160 --> 14:22.855
I'm sort of sucking
at explaining it right now.

14:22.995 --> 14:25.190
But you'll see it soon.

14:25.331 --> 14:28.164
Yeah, well, it sounds great.

14:29.702 --> 14:34.036
Mm.

14:34.173 --> 14:36.698
This pizza is nasty today.

14:36.842 --> 14:38.400
Gross.

14:38.544 --> 14:41.240
Ugh.

14:41.380 --> 14:43.439
Megan, how am I gonna afford
all this stuff?

14:43.582 --> 14:45.709
I'm-
You're gonna be fine.

14:45.851 --> 14:47.614
It's gonna work out.

14:47.753 --> 14:49.015
That's easy for you to say.

14:49.121 --> 14:51.055
You're not the one
with $84 in her bank account

14:51.190 --> 14:52.589
and a check to write on Monday.

14:52.725 --> 14:55.091
Yeah, but just relax.

14:55.227 --> 14:56.717
It's Wednesday.

14:56.862 --> 14:59.353
You know, if it's a big problem,
I can always call my dad.

15:01.133 --> 15:03.863
No, don't do that.

15:03.969 --> 15:06.733
No, look, he really
doesn't care at all.

15:06.872 --> 15:09.306
Look, I'm not saying
it's gonna get to that point,

15:09.441 --> 15:11.875
but if it does,
you're never gonna be homeless.

15:11.977 --> 15:13.638
Yeah?

15:16.715 --> 15:17.909
It's so weird and annoying

15:18.050 --> 15:19.642
the way that guy
stood you up today.

15:19.785 --> 15:22.652
I know.

15:22.788 --> 15:24.312
You're gonna find something.

15:24.456 --> 15:25.718
Okay?

15:25.824 --> 15:31.160
Did you go to the job board
at the intern office?

15:31.297 --> 15:32.286
That ham-faced girl,

15:32.431 --> 15:33.762
you know, in my class?

15:33.899 --> 15:37.426
Yeah, she said there's
good stuff there sometimes.

15:37.569 --> 15:38.763
No, I haven't been yet.

15:38.904 --> 15:39.928
Although it would be cool

15:40.072 --> 15:41.596
to get something easy
and under the table.

15:41.740 --> 15:43.970
That's what was so good
about the babysitter thing.

15:45.144 --> 15:46.805
Yeah, but it
could have been awful.

15:46.946 --> 15:47.935
You know?

15:48.080 --> 15:49.240
The kid could be from hell.

15:49.348 --> 15:51.942
You don't even like kids anyway.

15:52.084 --> 15:53.915
Yeah, I guess.

15:57.256 --> 15:58.689
You know what you should do?

15:58.824 --> 16:00.621
You should go around campus

16:00.759 --> 16:04.422
and rip down all of the other
posters he put up,

16:04.530 --> 16:05.758
and then nobody else calls him.

16:05.864 --> 16:06.922
How do you like them apples?

16:07.032 --> 16:08.294
That's good payback, right?

16:08.434 --> 16:09.423
Nah.

16:09.535 --> 16:10.593
What?

16:10.703 --> 16:11.795
It's genius,

16:11.937 --> 16:14.804
because then nobody else
will show up.

16:14.940 --> 16:17.033
No, I just want to forget it.

16:17.176 --> 16:18.165
No more drama.

16:20.346 --> 16:21.973
All right, then.

16:23.315 --> 16:24.304
You want to go?

16:24.450 --> 16:26.111
Yeah.

18:50.662 --> 18:53.096
Get a grip.

19:12.784 --> 19:14.649
What the hell time is it?

19:16.021 --> 19:17.784
Night.

19:19.124 --> 19:21.285
Oh, shit.

19:24.196 --> 19:25.720
Where's your friend?

19:27.666 --> 19:29.293
Who cares?

19:32.471 --> 19:34.996
Ugh.

19:39.711 --> 19:41.144
Someone called for you.

19:41.246 --> 19:42.736
Who?

19:42.881 --> 19:44.405
I don't know.

19:44.550 --> 19:47.986
Some dude, some guy.

19:48.086 --> 19:51.487
I left his number on your desk.

19:57.496 --> 20:00.363
Where?
Where did you put it?

20:00.499 --> 20:02.023
Chill out.
It's there.

20:02.167 --> 20:03.725
I just-

20:03.869 --> 20:04.858
I don't know.

20:05.003 --> 20:09.167
By your pens, maybe.

20:09.274 --> 20:12.175
When was this?

20:20.185 --> 20:22.415
Please leave a message
after the beep.

20:24.256 --> 20:26.554
Hello, this is
Samantha Hughes again.

20:26.692 --> 20:29.957
I got a message that you called.

20:30.095 --> 20:31.119
Samantha?

20:31.263 --> 20:33.390
Yes?

20:33.532 --> 20:35.363
Oh, thank goodness you called.

20:35.467 --> 20:37.560
Quite frankly,
I didn't think you would.

20:37.703 --> 20:38.965
I'm so sorry about this morning.

20:39.104 --> 20:40.366
Things were very hectic for me,

20:40.472 --> 20:42.963
and I got caught up in lots
of last-minute details.

20:43.108 --> 20:44.939
It was a bit of a catastrophe.

20:45.077 --> 20:47.568
It's all right.
Don't worry about it.

20:47.713 --> 20:49.374
I spoke with another girl
this morning

20:49.481 --> 20:50.743
who I thought was going
to work out,

20:50.882 --> 20:54.045
but she turned out to be
totally unreliable.

20:54.152 --> 20:55.642
And while I can
certainly understand

20:55.787 --> 20:58.483
you being upset with me,
I must be honest,

20:58.624 --> 21:00.455
I'm in dire need of someone.

21:00.592 --> 21:02.253
You mean tonight?

21:02.394 --> 21:03.918
Yes.

21:04.062 --> 21:05.154
It's very important.

21:05.297 --> 21:06.764
Um-

21:06.898 --> 21:09.332
I will pay you double
what I would have normally.

21:09.468 --> 21:11.402
That's $100.

21:11.503 --> 21:12.765
It's very simple.

21:12.904 --> 21:15.168
It wouldn't take even
much of your time.

21:15.307 --> 21:19.334
We would be home soon
after midnight.

21:19.478 --> 21:20.467
Are you there?

21:20.612 --> 21:25.140
Yes, um...

21:25.284 --> 21:26.273
Okay.

21:26.418 --> 21:27.407
I think I can do it.

21:27.519 --> 21:29.612
Oh, thank goodness.

21:29.755 --> 21:31.017
You're saving me.

21:31.156 --> 21:33.420
And I promise to make this
as painless for you as possible.

21:33.525 --> 21:34.514
That's okay.

21:34.660 --> 21:35.957
I can always use the money.

21:36.094 --> 21:37.288
Of course.

21:37.429 --> 21:41.422
Let me give you the address.

22:11.530 --> 22:13.691
- Hey.
- Hey.

22:13.832 --> 22:14.856
Thanks for the ride.

22:15.000 --> 22:17.127
I'm just your monkey
with a cigarette.

22:17.235 --> 22:18.224
Okay.

22:31.650 --> 22:33.709
The whole kit and caboodle
kicks off tonight

22:33.852 --> 22:35.183
just after 10:30.

22:35.320 --> 22:36.753
I know it's late
for some of you folks,

22:36.888 --> 22:37.877
but stay up.

22:38.023 --> 22:39.251
It's worth it.

22:39.391 --> 22:41.655
Be sure to find a good spot
where you can see the sky.

22:43.528 --> 22:44.756
Ugh.

22:44.896 --> 22:48.491
I'm so sick of hearing
about that stupid eclipse.

22:48.600 --> 22:51.398
It's, like, all anybody
can ever talk about.

22:51.536 --> 22:53.026
They're like, "Oh, gosh.

22:53.171 --> 22:55.731
"Are you gonna go see
the eclipse tonight? Buh."

22:57.042 --> 22:59.010
Oh, God.

22:59.111 --> 23:02.342
You know, it's not like
the moon's gonna explode.

23:02.447 --> 23:06.110
Although that would be
pretty cool.

23:07.853 --> 23:10.686
So do you want me
to come with you?

23:10.789 --> 23:12.757
I don't have to see
Mark tonight.

23:12.891 --> 23:14.791
He hates me anyway.

23:14.926 --> 23:16.587
No, it's okay.

23:16.728 --> 23:19.754
But I feel a little weird,
you know,

23:19.898 --> 23:22.799
just dropping you out here
in, like,

23:22.934 --> 23:28.804
in the middle of Jabib
or wherever we are.

23:28.940 --> 23:32.068
I mean, I had to look at a map.

23:32.210 --> 23:33.199
Well, don't worry.

23:33.311 --> 23:34.300
I'm gonna be fine.

23:34.446 --> 23:35.538
Okay.

23:35.647 --> 23:39.606
Okay, but I have
to tell you something.

23:39.751 --> 23:42.777
But you got to promise that
you're not gonna get mad at me.

23:42.921 --> 23:43.910
What?

23:44.055 --> 23:45.420
All right,
you can't get mad at me.

23:45.557 --> 23:46.546
You got to promise.

23:46.658 --> 23:48.489
- No.
- No-

23:48.627 --> 23:49.924
I don't even know
what it is yet.

23:50.061 --> 23:54.054
God-okay.

23:59.104 --> 24:00.298
Where did you get these?

24:00.439 --> 24:01.463
I'm sorry.

24:01.606 --> 24:03.130
You were upset, and I felt bad.

24:03.275 --> 24:04.264
Megan.

24:04.409 --> 24:05.433
I know, I know.

24:05.577 --> 24:06.566
I'm sorry.

24:06.678 --> 24:07.770
But look, like,

24:07.913 --> 24:09.505
it was-it was like,

24:09.648 --> 24:11.240
he was such a jerk
for standing you up.

24:11.349 --> 24:12.407
Yes, he was.

24:12.517 --> 24:14.109
And you were super bummed out.

24:14.252 --> 24:15.241
You were.

24:15.353 --> 24:17.685
And, like, we had
a really good idea.

24:17.823 --> 24:19.290
And I know that you
weren't gonna do it,

24:19.424 --> 24:20.482
so I had to do it, man.

24:20.625 --> 24:22.024
And I didn't know
he was gonna call you.

24:22.160 --> 24:23.149
How could I have known that?

24:23.295 --> 24:26.128
I'm sorry.
I'm sorry.

24:26.264 --> 24:29.859
Well, now I know why
I got the job.

24:30.001 --> 24:31.832
Nobody else called.

24:31.970 --> 24:34.131
Just please let me
stay with you.

24:34.272 --> 24:35.830
Please let me stay with you.

24:35.974 --> 24:37.771
I will be so good.

24:37.876 --> 24:40.367
I won't touch anything
or eat their food.

24:40.512 --> 24:41.501
I won't take your money.

24:41.646 --> 24:42.635
I just-well, I'll be there,

24:42.781 --> 24:43.873
and we'll, like, hang out.

24:44.015 --> 24:46.779
All right, okay.
I heard you the first 50 times.

24:46.885 --> 24:48.876
Can I come, then?

24:49.020 --> 24:50.851
Let's just wait
and see how it goes.

24:50.989 --> 24:52.854
They could be nice.
You don't know.

24:52.991 --> 24:54.117
No, I do know.

24:54.226 --> 24:55.989
Normal people do not pull
the kind of stuff

24:56.127 --> 24:57.617
that those people
pulled with you today.

24:57.729 --> 24:58.787
They just don't.

24:58.897 --> 25:00.023
Look who's talking.

25:00.165 --> 25:01.723
That's different.

25:01.867 --> 25:04.028
People make mistakes.
It happens.

25:05.370 --> 25:06.394
I mean, hey, they live

25:06.538 --> 25:07.527
all the way out here
in the country.

25:07.672 --> 25:08.832
So they're at least
normal enough

25:08.974 --> 25:10.168
to have real jobs
that pay tons of money.

25:10.308 --> 25:13.209
You think having lots of money
makes you normal?

25:13.345 --> 25:17.714
You've clearly never met
my family.

25:17.849 --> 25:20.409
Well, we'll see.

25:21.686 --> 25:23.654
Yes, we will.

26:08.099 --> 26:09.532
Hey, yo, check it.

26:09.634 --> 26:12.432
Volvo.

26:12.571 --> 26:15.096
Safest car on the road.

26:23.214 --> 26:26.206
Holy crap.

26:55.447 --> 26:56.505
Hi.

26:56.648 --> 27:03.417
I'm Samantha,
the babysitter.

27:03.521 --> 27:06.251
This is my friend, Megan.

27:06.358 --> 27:07.916
Vincent Ulman.

27:08.026 --> 27:11.621
Very nice to meet you both.

27:11.763 --> 27:13.822
Such beautiful girls.

27:15.200 --> 27:20.467
Please come inside.

27:46.231 --> 27:49.223
Have a seat.

27:53.838 --> 27:56.170
You're a doll for agreeing
to this.

27:56.307 --> 27:57.535
I mean it.

27:57.676 --> 27:59.644
Oh, it's nothing, really.

27:59.744 --> 28:02.076
I can't tell you how much
of a relief it'll be

28:02.213 --> 28:03.703
to get this night behind us.

28:03.848 --> 28:06.749
You know, we only arrived
in town very recently,

28:06.885 --> 28:08.910
and we really haven't had
a moment to spare,

28:09.054 --> 28:12.683
you know, what with the eclipse
and all.

28:12.824 --> 28:15.918
So are you a teacher
or something?

28:16.061 --> 28:17.722
No.

28:17.862 --> 28:19.557
I mean, not exactly.

28:19.698 --> 28:20.926
Just-did you know
both of you live

28:21.066 --> 28:23.398
in one of the most perfect
places on Earth

28:23.535 --> 28:25.025
to get a clear view
of it tonight?

28:25.170 --> 28:29.072
We heard.

28:29.207 --> 28:32.574
Yeah, this place is quite
the astronomer's dream.

28:32.711 --> 28:35.043
Are you an astronomer?

28:35.180 --> 28:38.115
No, not exactly.

28:38.249 --> 28:40.046
Samantha, could I have
a word with you

28:40.185 --> 28:45.248
in the other room, please?

28:45.390 --> 28:48.382
Um... sure.

29:15.053 --> 29:16.486
I hope you don't have
a problem,

29:16.621 --> 29:19.488
but you have to understand
that I am only paying one person

29:19.624 --> 29:20.648
for their time.

29:20.792 --> 29:22.783
Oh, yeah.

29:22.927 --> 29:24.588
No, Megan's not staying.

29:24.729 --> 29:26.060
She's just my ride.

29:26.164 --> 29:30.567
I don't have a car,
so she was just dropping me off.

29:30.668 --> 29:31.828
Oh, good.

29:33.171 --> 29:35.332
And please forgive me
for sounding rude.

29:35.473 --> 29:40.433
It's just that my wife
is very on edge

29:40.578 --> 29:43.672
about this whole situation.

29:43.815 --> 29:44.839
You're not being rude.

29:44.983 --> 29:48.783
I understand.

29:48.920 --> 29:52.014
Unfortunately, no,
I'm afraid you don't.

29:52.157 --> 29:53.852
Excuse me?

29:53.992 --> 29:56.460
Please sit down.

31:03.161 --> 31:04.355
You have to forgive me,
Samantha,

31:04.495 --> 31:08.431
because I've not been
completely honest.

31:08.566 --> 31:12.024
You see,
we actually don't have a child.

31:14.339 --> 31:16.204
We have a child, but he's grown.

31:16.341 --> 31:19.538
This job tonight
is not for a child

31:19.677 --> 31:21.338
but for my wife's mother.

31:22.614 --> 31:24.081
Oh.

31:24.215 --> 31:25.204
Hear me out.

31:25.350 --> 31:28.080
Mr. Ulman, um,

31:28.219 --> 31:30.551
I don't have any experience
with anything like that.

31:30.688 --> 31:32.178
I think maybe you should find-

31:34.893 --> 31:36.053
Okay, I'm sorry,
I'm sorry.

31:36.194 --> 31:38.185
I didn't mean to-

31:40.531 --> 31:43.193
Listen, this is not anything
like you're imagining.

31:43.301 --> 31:44.734
There's nothing medical

31:44.869 --> 31:46.200
that you would
have to do whatsoever.

31:46.304 --> 31:48.932
In fact, you don't have to do
much of anything and...

31:50.241 --> 31:51.640
I find this all a bit awkward.

31:51.776 --> 31:53.971
But you have to understand
I have only the best intentions.

31:54.112 --> 31:56.273
I've been putting advertisements
out for the past two weeks

31:56.414 --> 31:57.472
to get someone for tonight.

31:57.615 --> 31:59.207
But nobody responds
to elderly assistants

31:59.317 --> 32:00.750
or home care anymore.

32:00.885 --> 32:06.721
So I thought maybe "babysitter"
would get a better response.

32:06.824 --> 32:08.314
But to be honest,
it didn't do much.

32:08.459 --> 32:11.326
And like I said on the phone,
I only got one other girl.

32:11.462 --> 32:15.899
And when I told her the truth,
she backed out, so...

32:16.000 --> 32:19.401
I mean, I figure
it's all the horror stories

32:19.504 --> 32:22.064
that you read in the paper
and see on TV

32:22.173 --> 32:25.939
that have scared away
girls of your age

32:26.077 --> 32:29.672
from these types
of opportunities.

32:29.814 --> 32:32.647
Yeah, there's a lot
of weirdoes out there.

32:34.352 --> 32:37.150
You're right.

32:37.288 --> 32:39.188
And I sincerely apologize
for being dishonest,

32:39.324 --> 32:41.019
but what I'm asking of you
is not that different

32:41.159 --> 32:42.319
than what you expected.

32:42.460 --> 32:45.361
It's essentially
just like babysitting.

32:46.431 --> 32:47.420
I'm sorry.

32:47.532 --> 32:48.624
I appreciate your situation.

32:48.766 --> 32:49.790
I do.

32:49.934 --> 32:51.526
Okay, what will it take?

32:56.841 --> 33:02.040
How about if I gave you
another $100?

33:05.450 --> 33:08.544
Okay, okay.

33:08.686 --> 33:10.950
$200.

33:11.055 --> 33:13.489
That's $300 for one night.

33:14.625 --> 33:15.649
Please.

33:15.793 --> 33:17.283
