how important this is.

33:20.331 --> 33:23.323
$400.

33:31.809 --> 33:34.004
Hey.

33:34.145 --> 33:35.976
Megan.

33:36.080 --> 33:37.069
Jeez, come on.

33:37.215 --> 33:38.204
Hold on.

33:38.349 --> 33:39.373
Megan.

33:39.517 --> 33:40.506
Come on, wait a second.

33:40.651 --> 33:42.346
Are you out of your mind?

33:42.487 --> 33:43.681
Do you remember the game plan?

33:43.821 --> 33:45.482
The game plan was,
if they're weird, we leave.

33:45.590 --> 33:46.989
This is beyond weird.
It's mental.

33:47.091 --> 33:49.218
You know, they lied to you.
They lied to you.

33:49.360 --> 33:50.657
- I know, okay.
