33:50.762 --> 33:51.820
I know you're right.

33:51.929 --> 33:53.055
But it's $400.

33:53.197 --> 33:56.758
It's $400 for four hours.

33:56.901 --> 33:58.528
This equals first month's rent
and then some,

33:58.669 --> 34:00.694
