is sit inside and watch TV.

34:00.838 --> 34:01.896
It's too good to be true.

34:02.040 --> 34:05.203
Did you ever think
it is too good to be true?

34:05.343 --> 34:06.435
Megan, please.

34:06.577 --> 34:08.373
I need the money.

34:08.513 --> 34:12.882
It's so stupid.

34:13.016 --> 34:15.713
Ugh.

34:15.853 --> 34:17.616
I'm so mad at you.

34:17.755 --> 34:19.723
Look, you're being
a great friend right now.

34:19.857 --> 34:21.085
But this is huge.

34:21.225 --> 34:23.193
This one night changes
everything for me.

34:24.695 --> 34:25.753
Come on.
It's only a few hours.

34:25.897 --> 34:27.387
That's it.

34:27.532 --> 34:29.693
Just promise me you'll be here
by 12:30, and then it's over.

34:29.801 --> 34:30.790
Just promise me.

34:30.935 --> 34:33.699
Okay, fine, fine.

34:33.804 --> 34:34.793
12:30, right?

34:34.938 --> 34:36.634
Okay, yeah.

35:21.018 --> 35:22.645
Oh, God, Sam.

35:22.787 --> 35:25.779
You can be such
a fucking idiot sometimes.

35:57.321 --> 35:58.345
Oh, my God!

35:58.489 --> 36:00.047
Oh, my God.

36:00.191 --> 36:01.658
Oh, my gosh,
you scared the crap out of me.

36:01.792 --> 36:03.350
Take it easy.

36:03.494 --> 36:04.483
I'm sorry.

36:04.629 --> 36:06.153
I didn't mean to scare you.

36:06.297 --> 36:09.198
