36:49.941 --> 36:52.501
Did you just hide?

36:54.345 --> 36:57.246
Are you-are you not
the babysitter?

36:57.381 --> 36:59.372
No, I'm not the babysitter.
My friend-

37:39.590 --> 37:41.615
See, here we are.

37:41.759 --> 37:43.659
Half your payment in advance

37:43.794 --> 37:45.728
just to ease your mind.

37:45.830 --> 37:47.798
And here's a little more
