herself.

38:07.918 --> 38:08.976
She's quite independent.

38:09.120 --> 38:10.417
Most likely,
you won't even see her.

38:10.521 --> 38:11.783
But you need to be alert

38:11.922 --> 38:14.288
just in the off chance
that there's an emergency.

38:14.425 --> 38:15.414
You understand.

38:15.526 --> 38:16.754
Mm-hmm.

38:16.861 --> 38:18.590
