for my wife's benefit.

38:18.696 --> 38:20.755
She's, you know,
the paranoid type.

38:20.865 --> 38:21.923
But you get it.

38:22.033 --> 38:24.160
It all sounds easy enough
to handle.

38:24.302 --> 38:25.291
Terrific.

38:25.436 --> 38:26.425
Oh, right.

38:26.537 --> 38:29.199
There's-

38:29.340 --> 38:31.308
It's the number where we'll be

38:31.442 --> 38:32.636
just in case you need us.

38:32.777 --> 38:35.803
Oh, yeah, there's a number
on fridge for pizz-

38:35.946 --> 38:37.538
I already said that, didn't I?

38:38.549 --> 38:39.607
Yeah.

38:39.717 --> 38:40.775
If this wasn't screwed on...

38:40.885 --> 38:43.285
