38:43.387 --> 38:46.356
so I'm gonna get upstairs
and get the missus.

38:46.490 --> 38:49.891
And you just make yourself
comfortable.

38:50.027 --> 38:52.791
And I'll be back in two shakes
of a lamb's tail.

38:52.897 --> 38:55.889
Okay, thanks.

39:17.254 --> 39:21.554
I've done everything
you asked.

39:21.692 --> 39:25.423
Well, there's not going to be
any more mistakes.

39:25.563 --> 39:27.895
No, this one, she's perfect.

39:28.032 --> 39:29.226
We're not missing anything.

39:29.367 --> 39:33.235
After tonight, everything
will finally be complete.

39:33.371 --> 39:35.931
Please stop worrying.

39:36.073 --> 39:40.737
I have it all under control.

40:00.631 --> 40:02.098
Are you here for Mother?

40:02.233 --> 40:04.701
Yes, yes, I am.

40:04.802 --> 40:07.794
Wonderful.

40:10.975 --> 40:12.636
You're a godsend.

40:12.777 --> 40:14.745
It's nothing.

40:14.879 --> 40:18.747
Not to us, it's not.

40:18.883 --> 40:19.975
Well, I'm glad to do it.

40:22.420 --> 40:23.717
Hmm.

40:25.656 --> 40:26.816
Vivian Ulman.

40:26.957 --> 40:27.946
Samantha.

40:28.092 --> 40:29.081
Sam.

40:29.226 --> 40:31.956
Nice to meet you.

40:32.963 --> 40:34.430
What's the matter, Sam?

40:34.565 --> 40:36.157
Oh, nothing.

40:36.300 --> 40:37.494
I just-

40:37.635 --> 40:40.661
I thought your husband
went upstairs looking for you,

40:40.805 --> 40:43.569
and I didn't expect to see you
come in from over there.

40:43.674 --> 40:46.609
