sometimes.

40:46.744 --> 40:50.578
My friend Megan says
I'm out to lunch.

40:50.681 --> 40:51.909
I was downstairs
in the basement

40:52.016 --> 40:53.176
looking for my furs.

40:53.317 --> 40:56.343
I just can't get used
to this cold weather.

40:56.487 --> 40:58.648
I love the heat.

40:58.789 --> 41:00.347
We're from the desert, you know.

41:00.491 --> 41:01.480
Oh?

41:01.625 --> 41:02.614
Mm-hmm.

41:02.760 --> 41:04.421
What about you?

41:04.528 --> 41:06.086
Is this your home?

41:06.197 --> 41:07.687
Yeah.

41:07.832 --> 41:10.266
Well, it's more downstate,
but it's pretty much the same.

41:10.367 --> 41:12.927
I don't like the cold
much either.

41:13.037 --> 41:14.595
And now you're in university.

41:14.705 --> 41:17.196
You look awfully young
to be in college.

41:17.341 --> 41:19.673
Everybody says that.

41:19.810 --> 41:21.209
But I'm a sophomore.

41:21.345 --> 41:23.040
Oh, a sophomore.

41:23.180 --> 41:24.704
Wow.

41:24.849 --> 41:27.613
You could have fooled me.

41:27.718 --> 41:30.448
I bet the boys really like you.

41:30.554 --> 41:31.612
I guess.

41:31.722 --> 41:32.984
Hmm, you guess.

41:33.123 --> 41:36.183
Of course they do.

41:36.327 --> 41:38.795
A fine young beauty like you.

41:38.896 --> 41:42.957
I remember when I was your age.

41:43.067 --> 41:46.559
Your mother must
worry herself silly.

41:52.009 --> 41:55.001
Here we go.

42:01.752 --> 42:03.811
Ah, you two have met.

42:03.921 --> 42:06.412
Excellent.

42:06.557 --> 42:09.549
Yes, and she's delightful.

42:09.693 --> 42:10.751
I couldn't be more pleased,

42:10.895 --> 42:12.362
and I know that Mother
will feel the same.

42:12.496 --> 42:13.656
Good, very good.

42:13.764 --> 42:17.165
You see, things are working out
perfectly after all.

42:17.268 --> 42:18.257
And you doubted me.

42:18.402 --> 42:19.869
I know.

42:20.004 --> 42:21.938
You were right, and I was wrong.

42:22.072 --> 42:23.835
I'm sorry.

42:23.941 --> 42:25.670
Well, then let's get to it.

42:25.776 --> 42:28.210
Mustn't let the night
get away from us.

42:28.345 --> 42:29.505
Isn't that right, Samantha?

42:29.613 --> 42:31.547
That's right.

42:31.682 --> 42:34.674
Oh, and Mother
is very private.

42:34.785 --> 42:36.343
So don't be put off by it.

42:36.453 --> 42:37.715
It's just her way.

42:37.855 --> 42:39.015
Don't worry.

42:39.123 --> 42:41.523
