45:01.098 --> 45:04.261
Megan, it's me.
Pick up.

45:04.401 --> 45:07.529
You're still not home yet?

45:07.671 --> 45:11.437
Sorry if you're mad.

45:11.575 --> 45:12.701
All right, I'll call you back.

