01:07:46.395 --> 01:07:47.384
I'm sorry.

01:07:47.530 --> 01:07:49.691
Okay, have a good night, then.

01:07:49.799 --> 01:07:52.791
Thanks.

01:09:34.636 --> 01:09:37.629
Ugh.

